dc_description_s: Relief shown by 5 feet contour interval and spot heights. Map shows district; city, municipal or town; kiburgs or county blocks; final certificates (F.C.) and cadastral boundaries. Includes index to sheets. "Heights in feet." "The representation on this map of a road, track or footpath is no evidence of a right of way." "Cadastral boundaries as shown on this map do not in any way affect the boundaries shown in Registered Titles." "300-3-66." ©Copyright Uganda Government, 1966
